  1→Andes AE350 SoC Platform
  2→========================
  3→The AE350 AXI/AHB-based platform N25(F)/NX25(F)/D25F/A25/AX25 CPU with level-one
  4→memories, interrupt controller, debug module, AXI and AHB Bus Matrix Controller,
  5→AXI-to-AHB Bridge and a collection of fundamental AHB/APB bus IP components
  6→pre-integrated together as a system design. The high-quality and configurable
  7→AHB/APB IPs suites a majority embedded systems, and the verified platform serves
  8→as a starting point to jump start SoC designs.
  9→
 10→To build platform specific library and firmwares, provide the
 11→*PLATFORM=generic* parameter to the top level `make` command.
 12→
 13→Platform Options
 14→----------------
 15→
 16→The Andes AE350 platform does not have any platform-specific options.
